            <title>[LU-6342] DLC: implement lnet reload to make change in lnet.conf take effect </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6342</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Current the DLC lnet reload doesn&apos;t do any specific job, it would be nice to implement it. For example,  modify /etc/sysconf/lnet.conf (add a new network, etc.),  then run /etc/rc.d/init.d/lnet reload to make the changes take effect immediately.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
